{"tid":391592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"周杰否認強舌吻　林心如：品行自在人心","createTime":"2017-09-08T01:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T02:46:09.000Z","uid":48799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e320443ff6650a3e08836f340afe1478263e5f0","tid":391592,"uid":48799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"台灣女星林心如早年曾喺台灣綜藝節目《康熙來了》中爆料，指有次喺大陸拍戲時，某男拍檔硬將脷伸入佢嘅嘴裏，並要求同佢舌吻，嚇到佢即時花容失色！節目一出，隨即喺網絡引起熱論，有網友就將矛頭直指曾同佢合拍《還珠格格》嘅大陸演員周杰（劇中飾演「爾康」）。 <br />\n<br />\n相隔多年後，周杰喺9月6號晚上於微博發文否認傳聞，仲發文表示：「當初如果我真的強行舌吻某人，她為何不在當場提出抗議在她們的劇組裡（裏），難道現場工作人員和導演都是我的親戚？為何多年以後在她們省的綜藝節目中爆料？」隔咗冇幾耐後，林心如工作室就喺微博留言：「品行自在人心，多說無益。」疑似回應呢件事。"},{"pid":"6fae3a37c1b41d7b94546f667f993a73b49b073e","tid":391592,"uid":53672,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:45:04.000Z","msg":"原來周杰倫咁仆街"},{"pid":"f92903cb439fd9e6b4c17c810e795631932b4316","tid":391592,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:45:52.000Z","msg":"估唔到JJ係啲咁既人"},{"pid":"c3bc91ea5fb0955460262e3920763449c7826182","tid":391592,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來周杰倫咁仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7f0b4c3cc8a8145064076e2afdb00e0baaaba6","tid":391592,"uid":109728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來周杰倫咁仆街</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bc6152467f564b6a4d623e3d28da8fd85ee685","tid":391592,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"爾康真係世界級演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又係時候回顧一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c1c1eff7c7d36e72e171d3b28a6a3d89b9a8b9","tid":391592,"uid":61431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyT